27
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:12,400
What?

28
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:14,639
Six Divine Techniques - Blossoms in Disarray.

29
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:17,280
No longer bound by fixed, familiar patterns,

30
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:19,960
